<i>adjective</i>: 한가하다 [한가하다], 한가롭다 [한가롭따], 찬찬하다 [찬ː찬하다] <i>adverb</i>: 흐늘흐늘 [흐늘흐늘], 한가로이 [한가로이], 하늘하늘 [하늘하늘], 유유히 [유유히], 꼬물꼬물 [꼬물꼬물] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>한가하다 [한가하다]</dt><br>
<dd>leisurely; unhurried; relaxed</dd><br>
<dd>바쁘지 않고 여유가 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having time to spare without haste.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>한가롭다 [한가롭따]</dt><br>
<dd>leisurely; unhurried; relaxed</dd><br>
<dd>바쁘지 않고 여유가 있는 듯하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Looking leisurely without haste.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>찬찬하다 [찬ː찬하다]</dt><br>
<dd>unhurried; leisurely</dd><br>
<dd>동작이나 태도가 급하지 않고 조금 느리다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's behavior or attitude being slightly slow without haste.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>흐늘흐늘 [흐늘흐늘]</dt><br>
<dd>1. slowly; swayingly</dd><br>
<dd>힘없이 늘어져 느리게 자꾸 흔들리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of drooping feebly and swaying slowly, repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. in a state of being spongy; in a state of being pulpy; in a state of being squashy</dd><br>
<dd>물체가 단단하지 못해 자꾸 뭉크러지거나 흔들리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the state of being soft-textured so that it keeps swaying or cannot hold its shape.</dd><br>
<dd>3. leisurely; idly</dd><br>
<dd>멋대로 놀고 지내는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of enjoying one's life freely in a leisurely manner.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>한가로이 [한가로이]</dt><br>
<dd>leisurely; unhurriedly</dd><br>
<dd>바쁘지 않고 여유가 있는 듯하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Leisurely without haste.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>하늘하늘 [하늘하늘]</dt><br>
<dd>1. lightly; flutteringly</dd><br>
<dd>힘없이 늘어져 가볍게 계속해서 흔들리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of drooping feebly and swaying lightly, repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. (no equivalent expression)</dd><br>
<dd>물체가 단단하지 못하여 계속해서 뭉개지거나 흔들리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the state of being soft-textured so that it sways or cannot hold its shape.</dd><br>
<dd>3. leisurely; idly</dd><br>
<dd>어디에 매인 데 없이 한가하게 놀고 지내는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of enjoying one's life in a leisurely manner without being tied down to a job, work, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>4. (no equivalent expression)</dd><br>
<dd>김, 연기, 아지랑이 등이 조금씩 계속해서 피어오르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of steam, smoke, heat, haze, etc., rising up little by little, repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>유유히 [유유히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. leisurely</dd><br>
<dd>움직임이 한가하고 여유가 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>With a leisurely and relaxed movement.</dd><br>
<dd>2. far; old</dd><br>
<dd>매우 멀거나 오래.</dd><br>
<dd>Very far or very old.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>꼬물꼬물 [꼬물꼬물]</dt><br>
<dd>1. squirmingly</dd><br>
<dd>작은 몸짓으로 느리게 자꾸 움직이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of moving continuously and slowly with small motions.</dd><br>
<dd>2. leisurely; sluggishly</dd><br>
<dd>조금 느리고 게으르게 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of moving a little bit lazily and slowly.</dd><br>
<dd>3. (no equivalent expression)</dd><br>
<dd>몸의 일부를 조금씩 자꾸 움직이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of repeatedly and slightly moving some parts of the body.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>